---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Web & Network Design Services | GeneralSoft UAE"
  description="Professional web design and network infrastructure services including responsive design, UI/UX, and enterprise networking in the UAE."
  path="/services/web-design/"
>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <div class="logo">
        <img width="48" src="/img/logo.webp" alt="GeneralSoft Logo"/>
        <span class="logo-text">Generalsoft<span class="logo-legal">FZ-LLC</span></span>
      </div>
      <span class="lang-switch"><a href="/ar/services/web-design/">العربية</a></span>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li class="dropdown">
          <a href="#services" class="dropbtn">Services</a>
          <div class="dropdown-content">
            <a href="/services/custom-software/">Custom Software Development</a>
            <a href="/services/education-training/">Education & Training</a>
            <a href="/services/ai-development/">AI Development</a>
            <a href="/services/systems-design/">Systems & Software Design</a>
            <a href="/services/cyber-security/">Cyber Security</a>
            <a href="/services/web-design/">Web & Network Design</a>
            <a href="/services/mobile-apps/">Mobile Applications</a>
            <a href="/services/electronic-systems/">Electronic Systems</a>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li><a href="/contact/">Contact Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#about">About Us</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section class="service-content" id="web-services">
    <div class="service-section" style="margin-top: 120px;">
      <h2>Web & Network Design Services</h2>
      <p>We provide comprehensive solutions for your digital presence and network infrastructure. From stunning websites to enterprise-grade networks, our team of experts delivers reliable, scalable, and secure solutions.</p>

      <h3>Website Design & Development</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Responsive Design</h4><p>Modern, mobile-first websites that look great and perform perfectly on all devices and screen sizes.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>UI/UX Design</h4><p>User-centered design approach to create intuitive interfaces that drive engagement and conversions.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Custom Web Applications</h4><p>Feature-rich web applications tailored to your business processes and user needs.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>E-commerce Solutions</h4><p>Full-featured online stores with shopping carts, payment processing, and inventory management.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Types of Websites We Build</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Corporate Websites:</strong> Professional business websites showcasing your brand, services, and team</li>
        <li><strong>E-commerce Stores:</strong> Full-featured online stores with secure payment and order management</li>
        <li><strong>Portfolio Websites:</strong> Stunning showcases for creative professionals and agencies</li>
        <li><strong>Landing Pages:</strong> High-converting pages optimized for campaigns and lead generation</li>
        <li><strong>Blogs & Content Sites:</strong> Content management systems for publishing and engagement</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Frontend Development</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Modern Frameworks</h4><p>Build with React, Vue.js, Angular, and Next.js for fast, dynamic websites.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>HTML5 & CSS3</h4><p>Standards-compliant markup with CSS animations, Grid, and Flexbox layouts.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>JavaScript Development</h4><p>Interactive features, animations, and functionality using vanilla JS or TypeScript.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Performance Optimization</h4><p>Fast-loading websites with optimized images, lazy loading, and efficient code.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Network Infrastructure Design</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Network Engineering</h4><p>Design scalable, secure network topologies for offices, campuses, and data centers.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>LAN/WAN Setup</h4><p>Implement local and wide area networks with optimal performance and reliability.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Wireless Networking</h4><p>Enterprise WiFi solutions with seamless coverage, load balancing, and roaming.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Network Security</h4><p>Firewalls, VPNs, intrusion detection, and network segmentation for protection.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>Web Hosting & Cloud Services</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Shared Hosting</h4><p>Cost-effective hosting for small to medium websites with reliable performance.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>VPS Hosting</h4><p>Virtual private servers with dedicated resources and root access for flexibility.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Dedicated Servers</h4><p>High-performance dedicated hardware for resource-intensive applications.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Cloud Hosting</h4><p>Scalable cloud infrastructure on AWS, Azure, or Google Cloud.</p></div>
      </div>

      <h3>SEO & Digital Marketing</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Search Engine Optimization</h4><p>On-page and technical SEO to improve search rankings and organic traffic.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Analytics Setup</h4><p>Implement Google Analytics, Search Console, and conversion tracking.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Speed Optimization</h4><p>Performance tuning for faster load times and better Core Web Vitals scores.</p></div>
        <div class="feature-box"><h4>Conversion Optimization</h4><p>A/B testing, heatmaps, and user flow analysis to increase conversions.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container"><div class="contact-content">
      <h2>Let's Build Something Great Together</h2>
      <p>Ready to transform your business with cutting-edge technology solutions? Get in touch with our team today.</p>
      <div class="contact-info">
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">🌐</div><strong>Website</strong><a href="https://generalsoft.ae">generalsoft.ae</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><a href="/contact/"><div class="contact-item-icon">📧</div><strong>Contact Us</strong><br>Get in touch</a></div>
        <div class="contact-item"><div class="contact-item-icon">📍</div><strong>Location</strong><span>Ras Al Khaimah</span></div>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </section>

</Layout>
